title: DDFP 584: NFC teams not making the playoffs
itunes:title: DDFP 584: NFC teams not making the playoffs
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined by Cole Wright and Cynthia Frelund to go division by division in the "Davey Downer" segment predicting which teams in the NFC they believe are definitely not going to make the playoffs this season.
